<i># And yeah the human.</i>

1194
01:33:38.696 --> 01:33:40.860
<i># Tragedy.</i>

1195
01:33:42.283 --> 01:33:44.300
<i># Consists in.</i>

1196
01:33:45.494 --> 01:33:48.052
<i># The necessity.</i>

1197
01:33:49.248 --> 01:33:51.806
<i># Of living with.</i>

1198
01:33:52.918 --> 01:33:56.313
<i># The consequences.</i>

1199
01:33:56.464 --> 01:34:01.264
<i># Under pressure.</i>

1200
